org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.api.enums

Class DynamicSetParameter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.api.enums.DynamicSetParameter<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DynamicStringSetParameter, ImageStatisticsSetParameter, OverlapStatisticsSetParameter

    public abstract class DynamicSetParameter<T>
extends Object
    Parameter that acts as dynamic enum where a set of items can be selected Use DynamicEnumParameterSettings to define a supplier for the items. Alternatively, use allowedValues to supply items. allowedValues is preferred. If allowedValues is null, you have to use DynamicEnumParameterSettings.
